Name: Kamikaze Cube
About the game: Once a cube named Kamikaze decided to discover a dungeon but when he entered the den he realised that it wasn't a dungeon at all - it was the HOUSE OF DETENTION. Our hero, Kamikaze is a seasoned one but even for him these hell-like traps turned out to be a great challenge. Find the exit from this dungeon. Get your patience to die again and again. Features: - Hardcore - Minimalistic graphics - Achievements - Decent soundtrack - HARDDDDcooorree
